Uses of Package
edu.rit.http

  • Packages that use edu.rit.http 
    Package Description
    edu.rit.http
    Package edu.rit.http contains components for working with the Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP).
  • Classes in edu.rit.http used by edu.rit.http 
    Class and Description
    HttpRequest
    Class HttpRequest encapsulates an HTTP request received from a web browser.
    HttpResponse
    Class HttpResponse encapsulates an HTTP response returned to a web browser.
    HttpResponse.Status
    Enumeration HttpResponse.Status enumerates the status codes for an HTTP response message.
